托梅利亞

159
00:10:44.615 --> 00:10:49.308
在瑞典率先採取甜甜圈模式

160
00:10:49.615 --> 00:10:51.000
我們的甜甜圈模型\\Our work with the doughnut model

161
00:10:51.000 --> 00:10:54.923
開始從那裡落實生活品質計劃\\started in relation to adopting a quality\\of life program in the municipality

162
00:10:54.923 --> 00:10:58.269
並取代了環境和公衛目標\\and that replaced environmental goals and public health goals.

163
00:10:58.615 --> 00:11:00.385
此外，我們還有一個\\And then we had one

164
00:11:00.385 --> 00:11:03.577
涉及到環境的複雜領域\\complex area with the environment

165
00:11:03.577 --> 00:11:08.077
另一個複雜的領域則是公衛\\and then another complex area with public health

166
00:11:08.077 --> 00:11:10.577
當加入兩個複雜的區域時\\and when you add two complex areas,

167
00:11:10.577 --> 00:11:11.846
情況不會更簡單\\they don't get simpler,

168
00:11:11.846 --> 00:11:13.538
只會變得更複雜\\they get even more complex.

169
00:11:13.538 --> 00:11:16.231
在一個資源匱乏的小鎮\\So we started to think about how to handle this

170
00:11:16.231 --> 00:11:18.500
